1
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,720
Why are you guys here?

2
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,480
Do you even have to ask?

3
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,000
To destroy the evidence, of course.

4
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,440
The Grand Court of Justice is here...

5
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,760
...to investigate clues, naturally.

6
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,280
Where is your Lord Zhang?

7
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,720
Where is your Lord Shen?

8
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:00,720
Let's change the subject.

9
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,600
All this secrecy is annoying.

10
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,320
There's no time to hide it anyway.

11
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,160
They went to the Western Suburbs Imperial Tombs.

12
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:07,560
Heroine.

13
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:08,920
Why did you and Zhang Yi...

14
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:10,520
...gather The Four Directions to kidnap Li Chenyang...

15
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,320
...and trespass in the Palace?

16
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,600
What exactly do you want to do?

17
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:13,800
Be knights-errant.

18
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,240
A knight-errant must believe...

19
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,800
...that they can help others.

20
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,680
That is how one becomes stronger.

21
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:20,200
Even if one walks this path alone...

22
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:22,200
...someday...

23
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,840
...you will find like-minded people.

24
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:27,240
So you're looking for like-minded people.

25
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,120
That's right.

26
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:31,760
I want everyone to see...

27
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:34,080
...that people like me are taking action...

28
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:36,000
...and truly fighting against the darkness.

29
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:38,960
Heroine.

30
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:41,240
You are shining in my eyes.

31
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,920
I want to help you shine.

32
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:46,680
How about this?

33
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,280
I just got news from the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

34
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:50,040
First, save Zhang Yi at the Western Suburbs Imperial Tombs.

35
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,800
Then accept me into the Tang Clan.

36
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,480
We'll roam the martial world together.

37
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,520
Go south to kill Japanese pirates.

38
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,480
Join the Tang Clan.

39
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:58,280
Kill Japanese pirates.

40
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,160
That's not impossible.

41
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,720
But I drew a divination stick.

42
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:03,960
What kind of stick?

43
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:04,960
What did it say?

44
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,800
I'll tell you next time.

45
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:11,840
Then it's a deal.

46
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,600
When it's done...

47
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,120
...yours truly will handle the silver and expenses.

48
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,560
Yuan Ling.

49
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,520
You really have a big family business.

50
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:21,960
Did you hear that?

51
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,720
She's going to take me as her apprentice!

52
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:30,200
He doesn't care at all...

53
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,400
...whether his Lord Shen lives or dies.

54
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,200
Whether our Lord Zhang lives or dies...

55
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:35,640
...is also very important.

56
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,200
Could they be in trouble too?

57
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,960
Whose territory do you think this is?

58
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:44,440
How could there be only a simple secret door?

59
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,960
The last time it was this lively,

60
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,080
we were still a family.

61
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,360
My Godfather.

62
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,240
Since it has come to this,

63
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,000
why do we need to hide it anymore?

64
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:47,080
Actually, all these years I've been thinking,

65
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,600
if I could start over,

66
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,400
where would I choose differently?

67
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,400
After Lin Feng appeared,

68
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,280
to follow Godfather's wish to be cold-blooded to the end,

69
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:03,200
or abandon loyalty to live for love?

70
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,480
Is there any use

71
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:14,360
saying this now?

72
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,680
These are

73
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,920
of course just unknowable hypotheses.

74
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,400
But while I was trapped in the pain

75
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,320
of whether to place righteousness above family,

76
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:27,640
time and opportunity didn't wait,

77
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:30,080
pushing us all to this step.

78
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:36,720
On the contrary, I think the timing is just right.

79
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:42,280
Look at everything here,

80
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,600
full of pain.

81
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,360
Every one of them

82
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,320
believed in the faith he gave,

83
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,600
and died wearing the shackles he sent.

84
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,400
In the end?

85
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,720
Besides me, Wang Zhi,

86
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:57,080
who remembers their names?

87
00:07:57,880 --> 00:07:59,560
Remembers every single thing

88
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:01,200
they did for the Eastern Depot?

89
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,960
He didn't care in the past,

90
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,560
would he care now?

91
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,240
So,

92
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:12,840
everything should end here.

93
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:16,200
He should see what hell looks like beforehand.

94
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:17,600
Listen to

95
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:21,480
the sounds of souls here crying out for help.

96
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,760
Even he

97
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:27,480
should have a shred of humanity left

98
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:31,520
and recall something, right?

99
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,560
My good Godfather.

100
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:39,040
Look,

101
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:43,720
on the road to madness,

102
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,800
you and I are surprisingly unified.

103
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:59,240
The worst outcome of all this

104
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,400
is nothing more than this.

105
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,760
I always thought you all

106
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:06,240
knew but didn't ask,

107
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,520
knew but didn't listen.

108
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,080
I didn't expect

109
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:12,520
you were still confused, clear outside but muddy inside.

110
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,520
One Lin Feng

111
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,480
turned you all into something

112
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:20,120
neither human

113
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,880
nor ghost.

114
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:25,280
Lin Feng's death was his own fault.

115
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:26,560
If I didn't kill him,

116
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,800
he would have died anyway.

117
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,600
Heaven's Law.

118
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,400
This is Heaven's Law.

119
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,440
Look at you now,

120
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,840
it really proves that saying:

121
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:46,840
Heaven's Law is cyclical.

122
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,520
So,

123
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:59,160
I still have the strength and dignity

124
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:02,080
to make you accompany me.

125
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,000
Actually, if I could choose again,

126
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:10,360
I would rather die than go with the Eastern Depot people,

127
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:14,240
nor would I have any connection with you and Shang Hua.

128
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:21,360
Godfather

129
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,680
They are about to die

130
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:26,280
Do you really

131
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,640
not care at all?

132
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,680
From the very beginning

133
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,520
I pointed out the clear path for you

134
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,520
yet you all abandoned me

135
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:38,120
Just to prove yourselves

136
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:40,760
Wang Zhi did

137
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:42,360
Hua Shuoyue did

138
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:43,640
Even you

139
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,800
have been bewitched by Zhang Yi

140
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:48,000
Do you want to be

141
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:50,400
righteous knights of The Four Directions that badly?

142
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:51,840
Righteous path?

143
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,680
We are not on the righteous path

144
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:58,680
It is all just our obsession with you

145
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:00,200
Clearly

146
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,440
there were smoother ways to handle things

147
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,480
To keep Lin Feng alive

148
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:05,800
To let Wang Zhi take over the Eastern Depot sooner

149
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,440
Do you still not understand?

150
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,400
You are all a flock

151
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:13,000
of fledglings not yet ready for the world

152
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,240
Trying to fly high before you are grown

153
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:17,560
How could I entrust everything I have to you?

154
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:20,680
My hard work at the Eastern Depot

155
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,440
and the achievements I have accumulated

156
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:24,800
would all come to naught

157
00:12:26,880 --> 00:12:28,080
They do not understand

158
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,880
And neither do you

159
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:35,800
Fine

160
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,400
Fine

161
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:44,240
I understand you

162
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:48,240
But your achievements cannot cover your sins

163
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:12,920
Brother

164
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:19,840
I am sorry

165
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:21,680
Zhang

166
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:23,400
Zhang Yi

167
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:25,800
Zhang

168
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,000
Zhang

169
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:28,720
Zhang Yi

170
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,000
Go

171
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,080
Go, quickly

172
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:37,320
You go first

173
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:40,200
Leave!

174
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:45,680
Go

175
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:48,920
Go!

176
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:00,840
That is good

177
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:03,000
Do not cry

178
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:08,200
I...

179
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,080
Right now...

180
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,000
Right now...

181
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:15,120
how do I look?

182
00:14:17,920 --> 00:14:18,880
You look terrible

183
00:14:20,880 --> 00:14:21,640
Nonsense

184
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:23,840
Right now

185
00:14:25,760 --> 00:14:26,640
I must

186
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:30,440
look just like them

187
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:32,320
I have kept them

188
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,080
waiting

189
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:38,080
waiting for too long

190
00:15:29,160 --> 00:15:29,880
Youzhi

191
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:33,200
Do not disappoint me

192
00:15:41,880 --> 00:15:42,760
Come on!

193
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,240
In the end

194
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:50,520
you are still a soft-hearted whelp

195
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:53,560
I will deal with Zhang Yi

196
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:55,120
Men should not hit women

197
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:06,720
I forgot

198
00:16:07,160 --> 00:16:08,640
you are a eunuch

199
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:14,600
If Young Master Tang wades into these muddy waters

200
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,360
be careful not to get stuck in the mud

201
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:18,720
and be unable to save yourself

202
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:22,400
When there is an emergency in the martial world

203
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:23,240
if I am not there

204
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:25,440
how can I be considered a knight-errant?

205
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,360
Eunuch Lord Wang

206
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:30,040
please enlighten me

207
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:35,960
Clan Master Tang really has not changed a bit

208
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:37,200
Why did you come back?

209
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,360
To be a great hero, of course

210
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:40,720
Did you think I came to protect you?

211
00:16:41,920 --> 00:16:43,840
You fool blinded by hatred

212
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,160
No respect for your elders

213
00:16:45,800 --> 00:16:46,520
When this is over

214
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:48,000
let us go eat food from the Four Directions

215
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:50,120
It is a promise

216
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:09,320
I will help free you

217
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:29,480
Look

218
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:33,000
This is the price of betraying me

219
00:17:38,600 --> 00:17:39,280
Shuoyue

220
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,400
Shuoyue

221
00:17:41,520 --> 00:17:43,320
Why do you treat me like this?

222
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:49,600
Shuoyue

223
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:50,920
Shuoyue

224
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:52,800
Very well

225
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:57,880
The cycle of retribution is heavy indeed

226
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:19,520
Look

227
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:21,440
Look

228
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:35,920
Now,

229
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:38,320
it's time to settle our old scores and new grudges.

230
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,600
The Embroidered Uniform Guard is here.

231
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:13,440
Arrest Zhang Yi and the others immediately.

232
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:23,600
How could I not leave myself a way out?

233
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:24,920
But as for you,

234
00:19:25,760 --> 00:19:27,400
you have forced yourselves into a dead end.

235
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:30,240
We chose this dead end ourselves.

236
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:31,000
Damn eunuch.

237
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,480
Aren't you going to curse a bit?

238
00:19:35,840 --> 00:19:36,720
You old, undying traitor.

239
00:19:37,240 --> 00:19:38,360
We can curse even filthier.

240
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:45,640
Though the Embroidered Uniform Guard obeys the Eastern Depot,

241
00:19:46,080 --> 00:19:48,480
our true allegiance is to the Emperor.

242
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:51,880
I can go to the Imperial Tombs to protect His Majesty's safety.

243
00:19:52,080 --> 00:19:54,000
But I have no reason to go without the Emperor's decree

244
00:19:55,080 --> 00:19:56,920
to the Imperial Tombs to protect you.

245
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:04,040
Lord Yin.

246
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:06,520
If this matter is successful,

247
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:11,520
I will give you everything you want.

248
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,000
Lord Yin.

249
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:37,280
There is no need to keep Zhang Yi and the others.

250
00:20:37,480 --> 00:20:38,400
Execute them on the spot.

251
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:41,560
Gentlemen,

252
00:20:41,840 --> 00:20:43,880
my blade will give you a quick death.

253
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:46,720
For the sake of our acquaintance,

254
00:20:47,560 --> 00:20:48,440
I'll give you some dignity.

255
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:49,920
I'll leave your bodies intact.

256
00:20:51,560 --> 00:20:52,440
Bring the arsenic.

257
00:20:53,760 --> 00:20:55,320
Death by arsenic is too unsightly.

258
00:20:59,200 --> 00:20:59,920
Are you scared?

259
00:21:03,600 --> 00:21:06,200
Life is short, what does it matter?

260
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:09,600
With a true friend by my side, it is wonderful.

261
00:21:16,760 --> 00:21:17,800
Wait.

262
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:20,520
Youzhi.

263
00:21:21,440 --> 00:21:22,240
What are you doing?

264
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:39,160
Lord Yin.

265
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:41,160
What you want

266
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:44,120
is just to become the Embroidered Uniform Guard Commander.

267
00:21:44,600 --> 00:21:46,320
And no longer be controlled by the Eastern Depot.

268
00:21:46,360 --> 00:21:48,240
To take orders directly from His Majesty.

269
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:49,680
Am I right?

270
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:51,920
So what if I do?

271
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:54,560
You look down on me too.

272
00:21:57,040 --> 00:21:58,520
What kind of person my Godfather is,

273
00:21:59,040 --> 00:21:59,560
I think,

274
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:02,040
having served in the same court as him for years,

275
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:04,600
you should know better than I do.

276
00:22:07,360 --> 00:22:09,280
Do you really believe he will keep his promise?

277
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:11,040
After all, every person

278
00:22:11,040 --> 00:22:12,920
who has sat in the Commander's seat

279
00:22:14,120 --> 00:22:15,200
has not lived long.

280
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:16,760
So what you mean is...

281
00:22:18,600 --> 00:22:19,880
Just this one choice.

282
00:22:21,520 --> 00:22:24,280
My Godfather and the box in his hand,

283
00:22:24,280 --> 00:22:25,480
in exchange for your freedom.

284
00:22:26,280 --> 00:22:29,240
In exchange for all of our freedom.

285
00:22:38,920 --> 00:22:39,720
What do you say?

286
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:53,680
Guards!

287
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:55,840
Vice Minister of the Dali Temple, Zhang Yi,

288
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:58,200
and Commissioner of the Embroidered Uniform Guard, Shen Youzhi,

289
00:22:58,480 --> 00:23:00,280
have gathered evidence against the Eastern Depot Eunuch Lord,

290
00:23:00,520 --> 00:23:02,680
Shang Hua, for corruption and perverting the law.

291
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:04,560
Now, arrest Shang Hua immediately.

292
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:06,160
To be dealt with by His Majesty.

293
00:23:10,520 --> 00:23:11,280
Go now!

294
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:39,200
It is time

295
00:23:39,560 --> 00:23:41,520
to weed out the roots.

296
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:03,440
Tang Xi.

297
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:27,000
Tang Xi!

298
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:28,400
Tang Xi!

299
00:25:50,800 --> 00:25:51,520
Father

300
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:52,880
I want to save him

301
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:55,320
There are so many beggars in this world

302
00:25:55,560 --> 00:25:57,040
You save every one you see

303
00:25:57,040 --> 00:25:58,400
I am the Young Master of the Tang Clan

304
00:25:58,760 --> 00:26:00,080
To bear what others detest

305
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,880
To help others in their urgent need

306
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:08,520
Miss

307
00:26:08,760 --> 00:26:09,960
The change from the jujube cake vendor

308
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:10,680
You forgot to take it

309
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:17,240
My Lord

310
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:18,960
Money dropped on the ground

311
00:26:19,360 --> 00:26:20,440
Should not be picked up again

312
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:21,960
It is bad luck

313
00:26:25,800 --> 00:26:27,880
Zhang Yi attacked you today, Miss

314
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,280
Causing you internal injury

315
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:31,040
Please forgive me

316
00:26:32,360 --> 00:26:33,200
What are you doing?

317
00:26:33,560 --> 00:26:35,920
Money for the veil and medical treatment

318
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:38,280
It's all for you

319
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:39,720
Litigator Lu

320
00:26:40,720 --> 00:26:42,440
That sounded quite affectionate

321
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:45,360
Who says The Four Directions listens to just one person?

322
00:26:46,320 --> 00:26:48,280
Without me, the number one swordsman Tang Xi

323
00:26:53,520 --> 00:26:54,040
Young Master Tang

324
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:56,800
You cannot publicly attack a fourth-rank court official

325
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:58,600
Where is the key?

326
00:26:58,760 --> 00:26:59,640
How could the key be missing?

327
00:26:59,840 --> 00:27:01,040
How would I know it's missing?

328
00:27:01,760 --> 00:27:02,720
No respect for your elders

329
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:03,920
When this is over

330
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:05,400
We'll go eat delicacies from all over

331
00:27:06,600 --> 00:27:07,600
It's a promise

332
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:28,120
By the will of Heaven, the Emperor decrees

333
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:31,400
In the Jiachen month of the 18th year of Chenghua

334
00:27:31,760 --> 00:27:33,720
We govern the nation with filial piety

335
00:27:33,920 --> 00:27:35,240
Stabilizing the home and the state

336
00:27:35,760 --> 00:27:38,080
According to the Minister of the Grand Court of Justice, Pei Yuandong

337
00:27:38,360 --> 00:27:40,240
Vice Minister of the Dali Temple, Zhang Yi

338
00:27:40,440 --> 00:27:42,560
Commander of the Embroidered Uniform Guard, Yin Feng

339
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:45,400
Commissioner of the Embroidered Uniform Guard, Shen Youzhi

340
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:46,880
Who have jointly petitioned

341
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:50,040
Eunuch Lord of the Eastern Depot, Shang Hua

342
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,640
Has neglected his duties

343
00:27:51,760 --> 00:27:53,200
Abused power for personal gain

344
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:54,520
Embezzled public funds

345
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:56,040
Formed cliques for private gain

346
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,640
And plotted against loyal subjects

347
00:27:58,160 --> 00:28:01,080
The Eastern Depot guards followed his example

348
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:02,760
Truly displaying reckless rebellion

349
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:04,400
With rampant behavior

350
00:28:04,560 --> 00:28:05,920
Past deeds were improper

351
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:07,240
Causing future harm

352
00:28:07,560 --> 00:28:08,960
Those involved in these matters

353
00:28:09,080 --> 00:28:10,320
Deserve death for their crimes

354
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:13,120
But considering his past merits

355
00:28:13,320 --> 00:28:14,560
As a veteran minister of three reigns

356
00:28:14,960 --> 00:28:16,680
And his repentance is quite sincere

357
00:28:17,040 --> 00:28:19,920
All his family assets shall be confiscated by the treasury

358
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:21,200
After autumn

359
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:23,480
He shall be exiled to the bitter cold land of Fengling Town

360
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:24,960
To await further judgment

361
00:28:25,320 --> 00:28:26,760
Respect this

362
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:31,560
Your subject thanks Your Majesty for this great grace

363
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:39,160
The Grand Court of Justice has processed Shang Hua's case files

364
00:28:39,600 --> 00:28:42,000
Shang Hua's crimes have been made public

365
00:28:42,800 --> 00:28:45,520
The grievances of the persecuted loyal officials have been redressed

366
00:28:46,160 --> 00:28:48,880
The treacherous villains have been brought to justice

367
00:29:09,160 --> 00:29:09,840
Lord Shen

368
00:29:13,120 --> 00:29:13,720
Lord Shen

369
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,600
You need not wait for me here

370
00:29:17,040 --> 00:29:17,880
As for the prison visit

371
00:29:18,320 --> 00:29:19,840
leave it to Shuimo and Danqing

372
00:29:20,960 --> 00:29:22,160
My relationship with him

373
00:29:22,640 --> 00:29:23,920
cannot be compared to yours

374
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:28,360
Since I returned

375
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:31,440
aside from asking about the Eastern Depot investigation

376
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,360
I haven't wanted to say a word to him

377
00:29:37,240 --> 00:29:38,520
Autumn is coming soon

378
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,160
I just want to arrange

379
00:29:43,160 --> 00:29:44,120
his affairs in the prison

380
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,240
After all, the debt of upbringing

381
00:29:45,760 --> 00:29:46,480
cannot be abandoned

382
00:29:48,040 --> 00:29:49,000
If you do not wish to accompany me

383
00:29:49,520 --> 00:29:50,480
just wait outside

384
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:57,760
Godfather

385
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:01,320
I have arranged everything

386
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:03,360
regarding your daily needs here

387
00:30:04,120 --> 00:30:05,120
Though not like the manor

388
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,280
it surely won't be too bad

389
00:30:08,520 --> 00:30:09,680
If there is anything you need

390
00:30:10,800 --> 00:30:11,960
please feel free to ask

391
00:30:12,760 --> 00:30:14,280
His Majesty, considering your old ties

392
00:30:14,680 --> 00:30:15,520
has not made things difficult

393
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,040
Youzhi

394
00:30:19,080 --> 00:30:20,400
Why won't you look at me?

395
00:30:23,720 --> 00:30:24,360
Your son

396
00:30:25,520 --> 00:30:27,520
is ashamed of the debt he owes you

397
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:32,320
Raise your head

398
00:30:33,480 --> 00:30:34,880
and look at your Godfather

399
00:30:36,040 --> 00:30:36,920
Tell me

400
00:30:37,800 --> 00:30:40,480
why were you afraid that day?

401
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:42,960
Because I

402
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:46,200
fear you

403
00:30:58,240 --> 00:30:59,240
Don't be afraid

404
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:01,000
Raise your head

405
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:09,800
That's right

406
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:12,160
People

407
00:31:13,360 --> 00:31:15,400
only when directly facing fear

408
00:31:16,320 --> 00:31:18,160
can they be truly tested

409
00:31:18,960 --> 00:31:20,680
Reflecting on why one is born

410
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:23,200
for what purpose, to achieve what

411
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:26,480
exposes human nature completely

412
00:31:27,840 --> 00:31:29,200
What you would do

413
00:31:30,520 --> 00:31:31,880
how could I be surprised?

414
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:37,760
Because

415
00:31:40,240 --> 00:31:42,080
you are my son

416
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:47,680
No

417
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,760
I just felt

418
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:55,480
that following you any longer

419
00:31:58,280 --> 00:31:59,320
was wrong

420
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:02,200
You will understand

421
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:07,680
Only when one walks on the wrong path

422
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,640
can one truly find oneself

423
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:14,000
You

424
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:17,520
have never disappointed me

425
00:32:18,040 --> 00:32:19,320
After all, it is too late for you

426
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:21,200
to find someone in court to replace him

427
00:32:23,360 --> 00:32:23,800
No

428
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:25,720
someone to continue your life

429
00:32:34,360 --> 00:32:35,840
What a pity

430
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:37,920
A pity for what?

431
00:32:40,480 --> 00:32:41,680
To have met

432
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:43,120
people like them

433
00:32:43,560 --> 00:32:45,120
as brilliant as the morning glow

434
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,880
was the opportunity of a lifetime for you

435
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:51,000
Because of you

436
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:54,960
this morning glow turned into fireworks

437
00:32:55,600 --> 00:32:56,880
Fleeting

438
00:32:56,960 --> 00:32:58,320
Ceasing to exist

439
00:33:00,640 --> 00:33:01,880
If Eunuch Lord Shang thinks

440
00:33:02,080 --> 00:33:03,520
that because of these words

441
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:04,400
I will lose sleep at night

442
00:33:04,640 --> 00:33:05,520
then there is no need

443
00:33:05,800 --> 00:33:07,440
After all, this matter with you and Wang Zhi

444
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:09,760
is enough for me to boast about for a lifetime

445
00:33:11,560 --> 00:33:12,280
Zhang Yi

446
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,640
I wish you fortune and prosperity

447
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:16,480
and a house full of children and grandchildren

448
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:17,560
After all

449
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:19,480
they deserve it

450
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:42,960
Lord Zhang

451
00:33:49,520 --> 00:33:50,920
no need to take Godfather's words to heart

452
00:33:51,560 --> 00:33:52,720
He is most skilled at psychological manipulation

453
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:55,960
I understand

454
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:57,680
Lord Shen need not say more

455
00:33:58,360 --> 00:33:59,360
Since Lord Shen

456
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:01,320
has already made a choice once

457
00:34:02,360 --> 00:34:03,560
then there is no need to worry so much

458
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:05,800
Just live on in the way you like

459
00:34:07,520 --> 00:34:08,320
Lord Zhang

460
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:10,320
Some things

461
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:12,120
cannot be empathized with

462
00:34:14,720 --> 00:34:16,080
one only knows the warmth and cold oneself

463
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:44,720
If you like it,

464
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:46,640
then take it home.

465
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:55,560
Lord Zhang,

466
00:34:56,760 --> 00:34:58,000
are you planning to go to Huamanlou?

467
00:34:59,040 --> 00:34:59,800
This time,

468
00:35:00,920 --> 00:35:02,080
I could actually accompany you for a while.

469
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:05,520
Lord Shen, you've made progress.

470
00:35:06,240 --> 00:35:07,960
But I'm not going to Huamanlou this time.

471
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:10,520
After all,

472
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:12,960
the person I want to see isn't there.

473
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:04,840
She said she'd take me to the Tang Clan.

474
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:08,960
She said she'd take me south to fight Japanese pirates.

475
00:36:13,120 --> 00:36:15,320
Don't you heroes always keep your word?

476
00:36:15,560 --> 00:36:17,320
I was all ready to roam the martial world.

477
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:19,080
Isn't she number one under heaven?

478
00:36:19,200 --> 00:36:20,480
Isn't she the strongest?

479
00:36:21,160 --> 00:36:22,000
I'm sorry, Yuanling.

480
00:36:23,160 --> 00:36:24,400
I'm the reason she broke her promise.

481
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:27,880
Perhaps this is what people mean by

482
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:29,520
Heaven does not grant human wishes.

483
00:36:29,880 --> 00:36:30,520
Don't go.

484
00:36:31,680 --> 00:36:32,720
The capital is so big.

485
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:35,080
What will I do if you leave?

486
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:38,800
I don't want to say goodbye to you,

487
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:41,200
because we will meet again soon.

488
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:43,480
When we meet again,

489
00:36:44,160 --> 00:36:45,560
you might be a young hero by then.

490
00:37:11,080 --> 00:37:13,040
Fate has brought us to a perilous pass.

491
00:37:13,520 --> 00:37:15,720
Layer upon layer of rivers and mountains.

492
00:37:16,440 --> 00:37:18,480
Who knew the road ahead would be so hard?

493
00:37:19,120 --> 00:37:21,920
Tears soak my robe by the Xiaoxiang River.

494
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:23,360
Why is that?

495
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:25,320
You clearly drew the worst fortune lot,

496
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:27,560
yet you still do foolish things with us.

497
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:37,960
Shopkeeper,

498
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:39,320
a bowl of porridge and some pastries.

499
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:39,840
Coming right up.

500
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:43,400
Guest,

501
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:45,960
here is your porridge and pastries.

502
00:37:46,200 --> 00:37:46,760
Enjoy your meal.

503
00:37:49,400 --> 00:37:50,080
Officer,

504
00:37:50,560 --> 00:37:51,400
you dropped your money.

505
00:37:53,080 --> 00:37:53,840
Lord Shen.

506
00:37:59,720 --> 00:38:00,720
It seems Lord Shen

507
00:38:01,160 --> 00:38:02,720
was waiting here for me on purpose.

508
00:38:03,520 --> 00:38:06,200
I naturally have to keep my word to you.

509
00:38:08,680 --> 00:38:10,560
These are the latest tribute of late-ripening tangerines.

510
00:38:11,040 --> 00:38:12,400
In the court, besides you,

511
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:14,680
only the uneasy Consort Wan gets to eat them.

512
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:17,520
Lord Shen is thoughtful.

513
00:38:18,920 --> 00:38:20,320
These tangerines look sour.

514
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:21,840
I won't eat them.

515
00:38:28,480 --> 00:38:29,680
Perhaps to you,

516
00:38:30,560 --> 00:38:31,640
it is just a very sour

517
00:38:32,560 --> 00:38:33,960
or a very sweet tangerine.

518
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:35,640
You can choose not to eat it.

519
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:39,280
But for the tangerine,

520
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:41,640
being sour or sweet

521
00:38:43,080 --> 00:38:44,480
is its entire existence.

522
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:53,120
We follow different paths,

523
00:38:53,560 --> 00:38:54,480
so we cannot plan together.

524
00:38:54,640 --> 00:38:56,200
Lord Zhang hasn't tried the Embroidered Uniform Guard yet,

525
00:38:57,080 --> 00:38:58,360
so how do you know the taste doesn't suit you?

526
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:01,680
Lord Shen,

527
00:39:02,080 --> 00:39:04,000
you are imposing and authorized by imperial power.

528
00:39:04,560 --> 00:39:05,360
Unlike me,

529
00:39:06,240 --> 00:39:08,400
a commoner roaming the four directions.

530
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:10,320
How do we look like

531
00:39:11,240 --> 00:39:13,000
fellow travelers who can walk together?

532
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:16,600
Are you planning

533
00:39:17,920 --> 00:39:19,280
to leave the capital?

534
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:22,880
Why didn't you tell me?

535
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:28,080
Lord Shen shouldn't concern himself with where I'm going.

536
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:31,160
I just want to quietly lose myself in the landscape.

537
00:39:32,960 --> 00:39:33,800
Where do you plan to go?

538
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,320
Is there anything the Depot Guard doesn't know?

539
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:40,240
Otherwise, you wouldn't be waiting for me here.

540
00:39:42,840 --> 00:39:44,040
Actually, you don't have to leave.

541
00:39:45,080 --> 00:39:46,000
Nowadays,

542
00:39:46,200 --> 00:39:47,600
the Western Depot has been abolished,

543
00:39:48,080 --> 00:39:49,600
and the Eastern Depot has a new Eunuch Lord.

544
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:52,200
But for the common people,

545
00:39:52,480 --> 00:39:53,360
what difference does it make?

546
00:39:55,240 --> 00:39:56,840
If you are brooding over Tang Xi and the others,

547
00:39:57,920 --> 00:39:59,000
I can petition His Majesty

548
00:39:59,560 --> 00:40:00,520
to grant them posthumous titles.

549
00:40:06,240 --> 00:40:07,680
They don't care about such empty titles.

550
00:40:09,480 --> 00:40:10,760
But there are some things...

551
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:12,240
Just because I don't say them,

552
00:40:13,200 --> 00:40:14,120
doesn't mean I don't know.

553
00:40:18,040 --> 00:40:19,360
You always act with caution.

554
00:40:20,520 --> 00:40:23,040
And you haven't left our side recently.

555
00:40:23,520 --> 00:40:24,840
How did you meet with Shang Hua

556
00:40:24,840 --> 00:40:25,600
and reach an agreement?

557
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:29,440
Truly, cleverness can be one's undoing.

558
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:31,920
Shang Hua cannot come to Huamanlou.

559
00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:34,200
But what about the person he trusts most?

560
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:36,840
Zhang Yi,

561
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:39,160
even you have days when you are blinded

562
00:40:39,160 --> 00:40:40,720
by things right before your eyes.

563
00:40:41,280 --> 00:40:42,920
The change in some matters

564
00:40:43,680 --> 00:40:45,440
happens during the process, doesn't it?

565
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:49,480
You've been out of the palace for so long,

566
00:40:50,320 --> 00:40:51,680
why haven't you encountered a single pursuer

567
00:40:51,680 --> 00:40:52,760
from the Embroidered Uniform Guard?

568
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,280
Why could the Tang Clan elders

569
00:40:55,680 --> 00:40:57,440
find you so precisely

570
00:40:57,680 --> 00:40:58,920
and take Tang Xi away?

571
00:41:00,160 --> 00:41:01,800
Why was Lu Shijie's family

572
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,160
able to remain unharmed?

573
00:41:04,160 --> 00:41:06,680
Is it that you are powerful enough to cover the sky with one hand,

574
00:41:07,480 --> 00:41:08,640
or is it the other side?

575
00:41:13,840 --> 00:41:14,640
That day in the palace,

576
00:41:15,720 --> 00:41:16,720
you did hesitate.

577
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:18,280
You were hesitating whether to

578
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,400
kill us or not.

579
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,080
Later, you let us go.

580
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:24,440
You thought we would fly far away.

581
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:26,720
You didn't expect

582
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:28,720
that I would go find Hua Shuoyue

583
00:41:29,720 --> 00:41:31,200
and willingly return to the Imperial Tombs in the suburbs.

584
00:41:32,960 --> 00:41:33,640
So,

585
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:36,280
do not think

586
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:37,480
that everything they did

587
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:38,880
was meaningless.

588
00:41:39,840 --> 00:41:40,960
They lived freely,

589
00:41:42,320 --> 00:41:43,480
willing to give everything

590
00:41:43,880 --> 00:41:44,720
for what they cared about.

591
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:46,240
Drawing swords to help,

592
00:41:46,400 --> 00:41:47,240
protecting with their lives.

593
00:41:47,880 --> 00:41:48,640
That is how it is.

594
00:41:49,640 --> 00:41:50,360
It was I

595
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:52,800
who spoke carelessly.

596
00:41:57,040 --> 00:41:58,440
A thousand-yard dike

597
00:41:59,520 --> 00:42:00,640
collapses from an ant hole.

598
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:02,640
It's just that Master Shen

599
00:42:03,040 --> 00:42:04,240
does not consider himself the ant hole.

600
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:04,960
Master Zhang,

601
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:06,840
speaking of governing the state,

602
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:08,800
the highest wisdom knows the beginning,

603
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:10,480
the next knows the end,

604
00:42:10,560 --> 00:42:12,320
and the next knows the middle.

605
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:14,840
Without these three, the state is in peril, the self in poverty.

606
00:42:15,120 --> 00:42:15,960
The Classic of Filial Piety says:

607
00:42:16,640 --> 00:42:18,480
"To be high without peril is the way to preserve nobility."

608
00:42:19,160 --> 00:42:20,120
"To be full without overflowing

609
00:42:20,720 --> 00:42:22,040
is the way to preserve wealth."

610
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:24,160
"When wealth and nobility do not leave one's person,

611
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:25,440
only then can one protect the state

612
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:27,120
and harmonize its people."

613
00:42:28,680 --> 00:42:30,280
How do you know I am doing nothing?

614
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:34,280
Master Shen is very knowledgeable.

615
00:42:34,600 --> 00:42:35,720
I don't really understand what you're saying.

616
00:42:36,240 --> 00:42:37,560
Master Shen is brave and resourceful,

617
00:42:38,400 --> 00:42:39,720
willing to sacrifice everything

618
00:42:40,440 --> 00:42:41,280
for his own future.

619
00:42:41,960 --> 00:42:42,800
Little do you know,

620
00:42:43,520 --> 00:42:45,000
the karma between Shang Hua and everyone

621
00:42:45,920 --> 00:42:46,760
already appeared in

622
00:42:46,760 --> 00:42:48,280
Master Konghui's prophecy.

623
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:50,440
Godfather knew Master Konghui in their youth.

624
00:42:50,440 --> 00:42:51,320
They understood each other.

625
00:42:51,400 --> 00:42:52,320
The so-called heavenly secrets and fate

626
00:42:52,320 --> 00:42:53,640
are just self-deductions.

627
00:42:57,760 --> 00:42:58,440
Master Zhang,

628
00:42:59,240 --> 00:43:00,480
first, man proposes,

629
00:43:00,760 --> 00:43:02,040
then heaven disposes.

630
00:43:03,120 --> 00:43:04,080
Isn't that so?

631
00:43:06,560 --> 00:43:08,440
Master Konghui entered the heavenly secrets in a dream

632
00:43:09,040 --> 00:43:10,200
to let the world understand

633
00:43:10,680 --> 00:43:11,680
the logic of rise and fall.

634
00:43:12,160 --> 00:43:13,040
Although it is fate,

635
00:43:13,680 --> 00:43:14,440
it also depends on human effort.

636
00:43:14,960 --> 00:43:16,400
Observing the gains, losses, ups, and downs of all beings,

637
00:43:16,880 --> 00:43:18,480
one finds one's own way out.

638
00:43:20,520 --> 00:43:21,720
But what Master Shen said is also correct.

639
00:43:22,360 --> 00:43:23,120
Planning lies with man.

640
00:43:24,160 --> 00:43:25,080
If people don't change,

641
00:43:25,880 --> 00:43:26,640
how can the heavens change?

642
00:43:26,720 --> 00:43:27,200
Zhang Yi,

643
00:43:35,320 --> 00:43:36,560
we will meet again.

644
00:44:45,080 --> 00:44:46,160
Waiter, bring a pot of wine.

645
00:45:04,880 --> 00:45:05,480
Let's have one.

646
00:45:05,640 --> 00:45:06,120
Let's have one.

647
00:45:06,480 --> 00:45:06,960
Come on, come on.

648
00:45:06,960 --> 00:45:07,560
Drink up, drink up.

649
00:45:08,160 --> 00:45:08,880
We won't go home until we're drunk.

650
00:45:09,120 --> 00:45:10,400
Go easy on the wine if you're riding.

651
00:45:12,320 --> 00:45:15,240
A youth roams the world with sword in hand.

652
00:45:15,520 --> 00:45:16,600
To guard the mountains and rivers.

653
00:45:16,920 --> 00:45:19,480
Drunk in the mortal world, ascending to the skies.

654
00:45:19,800 --> 00:45:20,600
To protect the beauties.

655
00:45:21,640 --> 00:45:22,840
Now that is interesting.

656
00:45:23,840 --> 00:45:25,360
Now that is interesting.

657
00:45:25,480 --> 00:45:26,640
Now that is interesting.

658
00:45:26,640 --> 00:45:27,400
Young Hero Tang.

659
00:45:27,840 --> 00:45:29,960
Look at the bizarre sights ahead.

660
00:45:30,280 --> 00:45:32,560
It must be the demons' lair.

661
00:45:32,880 --> 00:45:34,760
Let me charge forward.

662
00:45:35,040 --> 00:45:36,600
And surely I will take those evil spirits

663
00:45:36,800 --> 00:45:39,000
And slay them all completely.

664
00:45:39,720 --> 00:45:43,520
What place lies ahead?

665
00:45:44,160 --> 00:45:48,840
Shang Hua's Fengling Town.

666
00:45:53,280 --> 00:45:54,560
Interesting, interesting.
